ly-irradiated interstellar sightlines will provide the optimal\ntargets for future C60+ searches.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Apr 2017 16:04:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 10 Jun 2017 04:47:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-26"}
