ence of non-cool-core, disturbed systems, as we observe\nat higher redshifts, can explain such behaviours.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Apr 2017 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Apr 2017 16:04:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-23"}
