\nsource, our results imply that LyC emission may be independent of Ly$\\alpha$\nemission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Apr 2017 04:03:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Aug 2017 00:48:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
