levant given the rise of distributed renewable\ngeneration and the computational challenge of operation and planning in such\nnetworks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Apr 2017 15:10:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Aug 2017 12:26:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 31 Jan 2018 15:47:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-01"}
